Package com.gaia3d.basic.types

Enum Class FormatType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<FormatType>
com.gaia3d.basic.types.FormatType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<FormatType>, Constable
public enum FormatType extends Enum<FormatType>
Enum for the different types of formats that can be used in the application. Each format has a corresponding extension. The extension is used to determine the type of the file. The extension is also used to determine the type of the file that is being downloaded.
